quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  26,169,"Olúwa mi, la èmi àti àwọn ènìyàn mi níbí ohun tí wọ́n ń ṣe níṣẹ́ (aburú).”"
  26,170,"Nítorí náà, A la òun àti àwọn ènìyàn rẹ̀ pátápátá."
  26,171,"Àfi arúgbóbìnrin kan tí ó wà nínú àwọn tó ṣẹ́ kù lẹ́yìn (láààrin àwọn tí A parẹ́).1 {1}",1:[Arúgbóbìnrin yẹn ni ìyàwó Ànábì Lūt – kí ọlà Allāhu má abá a - nítorí pé, nínú sūrah Hūd; 11:81, Allāhu - tó ga jùlọ - lo “àyàfi ìyàwó rẹ”.]
  33,22,"Nígbà tí àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo rí àwọn ọmọ ogun oníjọ, wọ́n sọ pé: “Èyí ni ohun tí Allāhu àti Òjíṣẹ́ Rẹ̀ ṣe ní àdéhùn fún wa.Allāhu àti Òjíṣẹ́ Rẹ̀ ti sọ òdodo ọ̀rọ̀.” (Rírí wọn) kò ṣe àlékún kan fún wọn bí kò ṣe (àlékún) ìgbàgbọ́ òdodo àti ìjuwọ́-jusẹ̀-sílẹ̀ (fún àṣẹ Allāhu). {1}",1:[Àdéhùn náà wà nínú sūrah al-Baƙọrah;  2:214 àti sūrah al-‘Ankabūt;  29:1-3.]
  33,23,"Ó wà nínú àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo, àwọn ọkùnrin kan tí wọ́n jẹ́ olódodo nípa àdéhùn tí wọ́n bá Allāhu ṣe; ó wà nínú wọn ẹni tí ó pé àdéhùn rẹ̀ (tó sì kú sójú ogun ẹ̀sìn), ó sì wà nínú wọn ẹni tó ń retí (ikú tirẹ̀). Wọn kò sì yí (àdéhùn) padà rárá."
  33,24,"(Ìwọ̀nyí rí bẹ́ẹ̀) nítorí kí Allāhu lè fi (òdodo) àwọn olódodo san wọ́n ní ẹ̀san òdodo wọn, àti nítorí kí Ó lè jẹ àwọn ṣọ̀bẹ-ṣèlu mùsùlùmí ní ìyà tí Ó bá fẹ́ tàbí nítorí kí Ó lè gba ìronúpìwàdà wọn. Dájúdájú Allāhu, Ó ń jẹ́ Aláforíjìn, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run."
  34,1,"Gbogbo ẹyìn ń jẹ́ ti Allāhu, Ẹni tí ohunkóhun tó wà nínú àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ohunkóhun tó wà nínú ilẹ̀ ń jẹ́ tiRẹ̀. Àti pé tiRẹ̀ ni gbogbo ẹyìn ní ọ̀run. Òun sì ni Ọlọ́gbọ́n, Alámọ̀tán."
  34,2,"Ó mọ ohunkóhun tó ń wọnú ilẹ̀ àti ohunkóhun tó ń jáde látinú rẹ̀. (Ó mọ) ohunkóhun tó ń sọ̀kalẹ̀ látinú sánmọ̀ àti ohunkóhun tó ń gùnkè lọ sínú rẹ̀. Òun sì ni Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run, Aláforíjìn."
  34,3,"Àwọn aláìgbàgbọ́ wí pé: “Àkókò náà kò níí dé bá wa.” Sọ pé: “Bẹ́ẹ̀ ni. Èmi fi Olúwa mi búra. Dájúdájú ó máa dé ba yín (láti ọ̀dọ̀) Onímọ̀-ìkọ̀kọ̀ (Ẹni tí) òdiwọ̀n ọmọ iná-igún kò pamọ́ fún nínú àwọn sánmọ̀ àti nínú ilẹ̀. (Kò sí n̄ǹkan tí ó) kéré sí ìyẹn tàbí tí ó tóbi (jù ú lọ) àfi kí ó wà nínú àkọsílẹ̀ tó yanjú.”"